<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5657> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5657" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Probably a Propraetor (Cic. Div. 1.68, praetorio imperio; cf. Dio 41.43.2-3). With Marcellus he shared command of the Rhodian section of Pompey's fleet (Caes. BC 3.5.3, and 26.2). See Cic. Div. 1.68; 2.114." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5517> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5517" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Along with Marcellus, he was in command of the Rhodian section of Pompey's fleet (Caes. BC 3.5.3). See also Cic. Att. 8.12A.4; Grueber, CRRBM 2.468; cf. Vell. 2.83.3." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5312> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5312" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "In command of the Roman garrison in the town of Carrhae (Plut. Crass. 27.7-8)." .
